title: The Townhall Weekend Journal for SEP-13-2013 FRI
description:
The Townhall Weekend Journal for SEP-13-2013 FRI



Friday, September 13, 2013


Obama ... Putin's Puppet
Weekend Journal



The Syria policy is an embarrassment.
 Former Bush speechwriter Marc Thiessen, Congressman Mike Rogers,
 and STRATFOR's expert on the Middle East Reva Bhalla weigh in.

 Dennis Prager concludes the show with a fascinating interview with a Holocaust survivor.
